race.description: You're On A Winner With Betdeluxe
race.comment: SWEET LOLLIPOP (7) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around this track in 23.56 to score two back then following on with a 23.95 win over 407m at this track. In form and looks the one to beat again. FARMOR BACARDI (4) has been in the placings at her last two runs, most recently when third (24.05) in a Free For All over 407m at this track. Can hit the frame this time. ZIPPITY ZEAL (6) had been in great form but was out of the placings last run, finishing seventh (24.92) in a Free For All at this track. Generally a safe beginner but buried in the ruck from a squeeze draw last time. Solid record here at the distance winning five races. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from four starts. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. JESSIE JET POWER (1) hit the frame latest (24.04) when third at this track in a Free For All. Has six wins already from this draw.
